  "translations": {
    "en": "Then the Commander of the Faithful (peace be upon him) said: \"Indeed, I have the knowledge of that, and Allah is Vast, Generous.\" Then the man, who was al-Khidr (peace be upon him), said: \"By Allah, you are right, O Commander of the Faithful. And above every possessor of knowledge is One more knowing.\"",
